Anemon::alter($input, $replace = [], $fail = null);
~~~

This is just a shortcut for `switch` and `case` statements:

~~~ .php
$input = 'bar';

$test = Anemon::alter($input, [
    'foo' => 1,
    'bar' => 2,
    'baz' => 3
]);
